---
// NewsletterSubscription.astro
// Anillo de suscripción: Obsidian -> Web -> Substack -> Blogger
---
<div class="newsletter-module">
  <div class="newsletter-content">
    <h3>Suscripción a la Mediateca ISAN</h3>
    <p>Únete a la red de nutrición intelectual. Recibe notificaciones de nuevos ensayos, transmisiones del Ágora y publicaciones cruzadas con nuestro Substack (@isanatelier) y Google Blogger.</p>
    
    <form class="subscription-form" action="https://isanatelier.substack.com/subscribe" method="get" target="_blank">
      <input type="email" placeholder="Tu correo electrónico..." required class="email-input" />
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Conectar al Cerebro</button>
    </form>
    
    <div class="platform-links">
      <a href="https://isanatelier.substack.com" target="_blank">Substack</a> • 
      <a href="https://www.isan-atelier.art" target="_blank">Google Blogger</a> • 
      <a href="/grafo">Grafo Obsidian</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.newsletter-module {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,20,20,0.8) 0%, rgba(40,40,40,0.8) 100%);
  border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-accent);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  margin: 3rem 0;
}
.subscription-form {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
}
.email-input {
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 6px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  color: white;
  width: 60%;
  max-width: 300px;
}
.submit-btn {
  padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
  background: var(--sl-color-accent);
  color: #000;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 6px;
  font-weight: bold;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: opacity 0.2s;
}
.submit-btn:hover {
  opacity: 0.8;
}
.platform-links {
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
}
.platform-links a {
  color: var(--sl-color-accent);
  text-decoration: none;
}
</style>
